snippet.title: G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra - Official Trailer | IGN Fan Fest 2024
snippet.description:
See classic G.I. Joe heroes in action, gameplay, and iconic villains in this latest trailer for G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra, an upcoming retro side-scrolling beat 'em up game coming to Nintendo Switch and PC.

In G.I. Joe: Wrath of Cobra, pick one of the real American heroes, gear up, and get straight into the fight in this retro side-scrolling beat 'em up - and make Cobra RETREAT yet again!

#IGNFanFest
